{
  "page": "Lord Blacktyde (father of Baelor)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blacktyde\" title=\"House Blacktyde\"><img alt=\"House Blacktyde.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Blacktyde.svg/50px-House_Blacktyde.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Blacktyde.svg/75px-House_Blacktyde.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Blacktyde.svg/100px-House_Blacktyde.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Blacktyde</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blacktyde\" title=\"House Blacktyde\"><img alt=\"House Blacktyde.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Blacktyde.svg/50px-House_Blacktyde.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Blacktyde.svg/75px-House_Blacktyde.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Blacktyde.svg/100px-House_Blacktyde.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Blacktyde\" title=\"Lord of Blacktyde\">Lord of Blacktyde</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Blacktyde\" title=\"House Blacktyde\">House Blacktyde</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Blacktyde\" title=\"Baelor Blacktyde\">Baelor Blacktyde</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Blacktyde</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Blacktyde\" title=\"Blacktyde\">Blacktyde</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blacktyde\" title=\"House Blacktyde\">House Blacktyde</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Greyjoy_Rebellion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Greyjoy Rebellion\">Greyjoy Rebellion</a>. He had at least one son, <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Blacktyde\" title=\"Baelor Blacktyde\">Baelor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His given name has not been mentioned.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Blacktyde_(father_of_Baelor)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord Blacktyde died during the <a href=\"/index.php/Greyjoy_Rebellion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Greyjoy Rebellion\">Greyjoy Rebellion</a>, fighting for <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a>. After the rebellion was over, <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Blacktyde\" title=\"Baelor Blacktyde\">his son</a> was made a hostage to ensure the Blacktydes' loyalty to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>, and taken to <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Blacktyde_(father_of_Baelor)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, The Iron Captain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Blacktyde\" title=\"Lord of Blacktyde\">Lord of Blacktyde</a> </b><br />?–<a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289&#160;AC</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Blacktyde\" title=\"Baelor Blacktyde\">Baelor Blacktyde</a></div>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404050030\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.307 seconds\nP